LongDescription: A small, hastily assembled platform which can mount two of the CM-4 series of cargo container missiles on the outside of the hull.
FlavorText:
ARGOSY EMERALD GREED
// - Bridge Transcript captured
Report edited

- CAPT Mateo: What is the meaning of this? We are completely within our right as a-
- 1SG Redding: You are Captain Gabriel Mateo? Pursuant to Decision 7 by Armo Blackwood, Baron of Pyxis, this vessel is now under the executive command of the Outer Systems- [Redding is interrupted by Mateo and crew]
- Mateo: What the hell are you talking about?
- Redding: - Protectorate Navy, under Admiral Caesar Constantine. You are to immediately relinquish command, transfer appropriate access keys, and provide forthwith a manifest of your personnel and attached cargo including any containers, empty or otherwise.
[Angry shouting, many expletives]
- Mateo: This is inexcusable! You have no right to take our ship! I did not spend years of my life building this ship for it to be taken by some warmongering son of a bi-
- Redding: You may report to Lieutenant Valorie Rix regarding safe transportation of your possessions. If you refuse to cooperate, you will be forci-
- Mateo: [Expletive removed] you, you ignorant [Expletive removed]! I will not stand by while you- get off of me!
- Redding: Get them off this ship. Mark those containers for Ordinance.
